# Tofu Milanese

Based on [https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1024089-tofu-milanese](https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1024089-tofu-milanese) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251119101652/https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1024089-tofu-milanese))

